params.vToken: The vToken used by the vault

Initialized(uint8).details: Triggered when the contract has been initialized or reinitialized.

acceptOwnership().details: The new owner accepts the ownership transfer.

createERC4626(address).custom:error: ZeroAddressNotAllowed is thrown when the vToken address is zeroVenusERC4626Factory__InvalidVToken is thrown when the provided vToken is not supported by the poolRegistryVenusERC4626Factory__ERC4626AlreadyExists is thrown when this factory already created a VenusERC4626 for the provided vToken
createERC4626(address).custom:event: CreateERC4626 is emitted when the ERC4626 wrapper is created

params.vToken: The vToken address to create the vault

params.loopsLimitNumber: The loops limit for the MaxLoopsLimit helper
params.poolRegistryAddress: Address of the Pool Registry contract
params.venusERC4626Implementation: Address of the VenusERC4626 implementation contract

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

pendingOwner().details: Returns the address of the pending owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

setAccessControlManager(address).details: Admin function to set address of AccessControlManager

params.accessControlManager_: The new address of the AccessControlManager

setRewardRecipient(address).custom:error: ZeroAddressNotAllowed is thrown when the new recipient address is zero
setRewardRecipient(address).custom:event: RewardRecipientUpdated is emitted when the reward recipient address is updated

params.newRecipient: The address of the new reward recipient

transferOwnership(address).details: Starts the ownership transfer of the contract to a new account. Replaces the pending transfer if there is one. Can only be called by the current owner.

MaxLoopsLimitExceeded(uint256,uint256).notice: Thrown an error on maxLoopsLimit exceeds for any loop

Unauthorized(address,address,string).notice: Thrown when the action is prohibited by AccessControlManager

VenusERC4626Factory__ERC4626AlreadyExist.notice: Thrown when a VenusERC4626 already exists for the provided vToken

VenusERC4626Factory__InvalidVToken().notice: Thrown when the provided vToken is not registered in PoolRegistry

ZeroAddressNotAllowed().notice: Thrown if the supplied address is a zero address where it is not allowed

CreateERC4626(address,address).notice: Emitted when a new ERC4626 vault has been created

MaxLoopsLimitUpdated(uint256,uint256).notice: Emitted when max loops limit is set

NewAccessControlManager(address,address).notice: Emitted when access control manager contract address is changed

RewardRecipientUpdated(address,address).notice: Emitted when the reward recipient address is updated.

SALT().notice: A constant salt value used for deterministic contract deployment

accessControlManager().notice: Returns the address of the access control manager contract

beacon().notice: The beacon contract for VenusERC4626 proxies

computeVaultAddress(address).notice: Predicts the vault address for a given vToken

createERC4626(address).notice: Creates a VenusERC4626 vault for a given asset and comptroller

rewardRecipient().notice: The address that will receive the liquidity mining rewards

setMaxLoopsLimit(uint256).notice: Set the limit for the loops can iterate to avoid the DOS

setRewardRecipient(address).notice: Sets a new reward recipient address
